Description: Statistics generator for IRC logs
DescDetail: <<
Xstat is an IRC statistics generator which generates a Web page of
statistics from an IRC log file. It is useful for channel ops who
want to publish their channel information and statistics online. It
also includes a front-end Gtk interface. 
<<
